channel.title: Warning for P16 Users!
channel.description: Don't add anymore handlers, Like login handlers, and such. And put the WorldObjects.cfg that you should have, into the CFG folder. Then another note: Dont use too big server printouts, it makes your server real hard to boot, and it will have MAJOR lag. Soon i'll be putting online a P16 Lite version, with all un-needed crap out of it. Just a little warning if u have a P16 source and u want a good server ^_^
